      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 37.1 - 老子 37.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 37.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>道常無為而無不為。侯王若能守之，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Dao in its regular course does nothing (for the sake of doing it), and so there is nothing which it does not do.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
