      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 37.4 - 老子 37.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 37.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>萬物將自化。化而欲作，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If princes and kings were able to maintain it, all things would of themselves be transformed by them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
